taskKey="com.codegym.task.task07.task0714"\n\nWords in reverse


Read 5 words from the keyboard and add them to a list of strings. Remove the 3rd item in the list, and then display the remaining items in reverse order.


Requirements:
1.	Declare a ArrayList&lt;String&gt; variable and immediately initialize it.
2.	Read 5 lines from the keyboard and add them to the list.
3.	Remove the third element of list.
4.	Display the items on the screen, each on a new line.
5.	The display order must be reversed.


